Package com.team7.cmput301.android.theirisproject.task

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Callback<M>
    Callback is an interface that allows AsyncTasks to call functions from the main thread after the async task is finished.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddBodyPhotoTask
    AddBodyPhotoTask asynchronously adds a bodyphoto to the database
    AddCommentTask
    AddCommentTask adds a comment asynchronously on another thread and will return the result status: success or error
    AddPatientTask
    AddPatientTask takes in two parameters, the Patient's e-mail and whether or not we are adding the Patient by importing a Contact or not If the given username is not a registered user, task returns false onCompletion Otherwise, the Patient's ID is added to the Care Provider's list of Patients and vice versa.
    AddProblemTask
    AddProblemTask is an AsyncTask that sends a POST request to our database with the new problem data.
    AddRecordPhotoTask
    Asynchronously adds a single Record Photo to elasticsearch DB.
    AddRecordTask
    AddRecordTask is an async task that will dispatch when the user submits a new record and the task will add it to the database returning its id
    AddTransferCodeTask
    AddTransferCodeTask takes in a code (automatically generated) and makes an entry for it in the index that has type 'code' within Elasticsearch Returns true if adding the code is a success, false otherwise
    BulkUpdateTask
    Periodically checks internet connection, and bulk updates models that have changed when internet connection detected.
    CacheBodyPhotoTask
    CacheBodyPhotoTask will run in the background to save body photos in the apps internal storage for quicker loading of images on BodyPhotoListActivity
    DeleteBodyPhotoTask
    Deletes a single Body Photo from elasticsearch and disk
    DeleteProblemTask
    DeleteProblemTask asynchronously deletes a problem from the database
    DeleteRecordPhotoTask
    Deletes a single Record Photo from elasticsearch
    DeleteRecordTask  
    DeleteTransferCodeTask
    DeleteTransferCodeTask first checks if the given code exists in the DB, and if it is, deletes it (the code is now used) and returns the username for the transferring user to successfully log them in
    EditProblemTask
    EditProblemTask is an AsyncTask that sends a POST request to our database with the edited problem data.
    EditProfileTask
    Task that is used to update the given username's email and phone number to the newly given email and phone number
    EditRecordTask
    Tries to update specified Record in elasticsearch using its ID.
    GetBodyPhotoTask
    GetBodyPhotoTask will asynchronously retrieve body photos that are related to the user.
    GetPatientListByContactTask
    Takes in a List of Contacts and returns a List of Patients who either have a phone number or e-mail registered in the app that is also part of the Contacts list
    GetPatientListTask
    GetPatientListTask is responsible for taking in a careProviderId and returning a List of Patients representing all Patients that Care Provider has registered.
    GetProblemListTask
    GetProblemListTask is a function that asynchronously retrieves data from our Elasticsearch database.
    GetProblemTask
    GetProblemTask asynchronously gets a problem from the database first it queries the primitive fields of a problem.
    GetProblemTask.GetCommentTask
    GetCommentTask is a nested AsyncTask that will run concurrently with GetProblemTask to speed up our process in retrieving data for a problem.
    GetRecordListTask
    Asynchronously searches ElasticSearch DB to ultimately make a RecordList
    GetRecordPhotosTask
    GetRecordPhotosTask queries the record photos associated to the problem
    GetRecordPhotoTask
    GetRecordPhotoTask queries the record photos associated to the record
    GetRecordTask
    GetRecordTask is an async task that fetches a Record model from the database given a record id
    GetTransferCodeTask
    GetTransferCodeTask returns the transfer code for the given user if it already exists, null otherwise
    GetUserDataTask
    Asynchronously gets all of a User's data.
    LoginTask  
    RegisterTask
    RegisterTask is an AsyncTask that asynchronously registers the given user into the database.
    SearchBodyLocationTask
    SearchBodyLocationTask searches the database for problems/records related to a bodyphoto with a label given
    SearchGeoLocationTask
    SearchGeoLocationTask searches for Records and their associated Problems with a given latitude,longitude input
    SearchKeywordTask<M>
    SearchKeywordTask searches problems and records based on the keywords given
    SearchProblemsByRecordsTask
    SearchProblemsByRecordsTask gets a list of records and will return a list of all problems associated with the records
    SleepTask
